{
  "stem": "21786.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That is, I mean, as we say, one hand washes the other hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I gave them their laundry, and I am left in peace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It becomes a kind of a deadly game, but a game which feeds people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A little funnier story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The conditions were so that people were dying, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My comrades were dying of malnutrition and terrible, horrible, absolutely horrendous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They kept there for nine hours, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And let's say carrying cement bags or working there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They are rebuilding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In fact, it was something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The mortality that was really bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "People didn't die, but people were so weak that we had to rotate them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was some kind of a primitive lazaretto, and the head of the lazaretto was also a German prison-- I mean, Aryan German prisoner-- who was in the camp, for he was gay.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So-- but something human was left in him in spite of his long imprisonment and really torture he went through, so that we, always-- the sickest we kept in this kind of lazaretto.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so we tried simply to rotate the people so that they would survive as long as they could.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so it happened-- two things happened to me, which were quite significant for my existence there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "One of them was that we had the Romanian SS-- I mean, Romanian/German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Volks German, V-O-L-K-S, meaning of the folk, of the people, of the German origin-- who was especially stupid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "His name was Romejko, R-O-M-E-J-K-O.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he was a bully.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Oh, not that he would kill anybody, but he liked really to smack people and to kick people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we had-- we-- we got him tamed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
